{"title":"莫让青春化作灰","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":7,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫让青春化作灰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下面这首诗，原载北京某大学的墙报，是劝一位在彷徨中尚未决心转变的右派分子的。现转载于此，并隐去真实姓名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欣闻×君举义旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"败子回头胜金玉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"簟食壶浆待路旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只听雷声不见雨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躲躲闪闪暗张弦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪闪躲躲伪造作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭哭啼啼放悲声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啼啼哭哭畏汤药。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×××，×××，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好医不怜病人泪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悬崖勒马速回头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫让青春化作灰。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}